üîÑ Implementation Roadmap:

```python
def deploy_maya_supply_chain(existing_logistics_infrastructure):
    deployment_phases = {
        'phase_1': 'Supplier Foundation - Raw Material & Partner Networks',
        'phase_2': 'Production Platform - Manufacturing & Quality Coordination',
        'phase_3': 'Distribution Temple - Logistics & Inventory Management',
        'phase_4': 'Demand Observatory - Forecasting & Strategic Planning',
        'phase_5': 'Sacred Integration - Holistic Supply Chain Ecosystem'
    }
    
    supply_chain_system = KuhulKaySupplyChain(existing_logistics_infrastructure)
    return supply_chain_system.comprehensive_supply_chain_management("global_operations")
```

This Maya-inspired supply chain system represents a transformative shift from linear, fragile supply chains to resilient, cyclical networks - from reactive problem-solving to proactive pattern recognition - and from isolated optimization to ecosystem harmony. Exactly what modern supply chains need in an era of constant disruption and complexity!
